osyfe.data

Class Data

  • java.lang.Object
    • osyfe.data.Data
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    DArray, DList, DMap, DPrimitives.DByte, DPrimitives.DByteArray, DPrimitives.DDouble, DPrimitives.DDoubleArray, DPrimitives.DFloat, DPrimitives.DFloatArray, DPrimitives.DInt, DPrimitives.DIntArray, DPrimitives.DLong, DPrimitives.DLongArray, DPrimitives.DShort, DPrimitives.DShortArray, DPrimitives.DString

    public abstract class Data
extends java.lang.Object
    The superclass for data structure wrappers that are streamable. Lesson: Generics in Java sucks.
    Note that the data hierarchy can not contain cyclic references.
